{
  "stem": "5761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was my younger brother, myself, and my oldest sister as a supervisor, and my nephew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They tried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But they were caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One sister was put in jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my other-- the rest of the family managed to escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they remained in Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He felt it's the first opportunity that some of the family should go abroad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they knew it, sooner or later, they will join to leave Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he felt quicker is better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is-- listen, we, we were about 1,200 children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't realize what happening-- nice boat, English boat, supervised, taking care of us beautifully.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were saying that we are going to a Polish camp in Tehran, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in Iran, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Naturally, it took about eight months till we got there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The first step that we ended was in India, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which is now-- it was the, the city Karachi, which is now Pakistan.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took us to the Polish camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed there under the Polish army supervision for many months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just nothing-- slept in the tent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a few times, they took as with buses to see this, you know, the town and the zoo, took us around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was in a sanded area where military camps normally are put up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were like, you know, overdosed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going on, separated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were children different ages, I would say from two years and up, up to 15, 16-year-old kids.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bigger kids used to take care of the littler ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was not a happy time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I cannot say good memories.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
